                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A vloriak's saliva causes metal to rust rapidly. If it succeeds at a tongue Strike or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Disarm] attempt, the vloriak deals @Damage[2d6[untyped]] damage (doubled on a critical hit) to a metal item the target is wearing or holding, ignoring its Hardness. If the vloriak hits an unattended metal item, the item takes this damage automatically. If a creature uses the Shield Block reaction with a metal shield against a tongue attack, the shield is automatically broken, but no other item is rusted on that attack.</p>"
